# Functions
#
# XQuery 1.0, XPath 2.0, and XSLT 2.0 share the same functions library.
# XSLT includes over 100 built-in functions. There are functions for 
# string values, numeric values, date and time comparison, node and 
# QName manipulation, sequence manipulation, Boolean values, and more.

# XSLT 2.0
http://www.w3schools.com/xpath/xpath_functions.asp
http://www.w3schools.com/xsl/xsl_functions.asp

